00:37:25.020 --> 00:37:26.380
I bet, it has gone up.

00:37:26.380 --> 00:37:30.390
There's more opportunities for
gambling and it's gone up.

00:37:30.390 --> 00:37:37.590
1.1% of men are compulsive
gamblers and 0.5% of women.

00:37:37.590 --> 00:37:40.530
This is another male trait.

00:37:40.530 --> 00:37:43.250
Somehow men are more vulnerable
to compulsive

00:37:43.250 --> 00:37:44.640
gambling than women.

00:37:44.640 --> 00:37:47.420
But it's only a factor
of 2-to-1.

00:37:47.420 --> 00:37:50.890
But it's an addiction
that happens that

00:37:50.890 --> 00:37:52.740
distorts people's thinking.

00:37:52.740 --> 00:37:55.410
And it's such an addiction that
we have an organization

00:37:55.410 --> 00:37:59.980
called Gamblers Anonymous that
helps people with this.

00:37:59.980 --> 00:38:02.270
It ruins people's lives.

00:38:02.270 --> 00:38:04.980
People end up getting a divorce,
because you can't

00:38:04.980 --> 00:38:08.360
stay with someone, married to
someone, who is squandering

00:38:08.360 --> 00:38:09.790
the family money.

00:38:09.790 --> 00:38:10.230
They do it.

00:38:10.230 --> 00:38:13.580
They end up sneaking around to
gamble, like drinkers sneak

00:38:13.580 --> 00:38:14.850
around for the next drink.

00:38:17.490 --> 00:38:22.890
Gambling behavior, it seems to
be associated psychologically

00:38:22.890 --> 00:38:26.700
with a self-image, a sense of
who I am and why I'm an

00:38:26.700 --> 00:38:27.900
important and good person.

00:38:27.900 --> 00:38:29.860
A sense of competence.

00:38:29.860 --> 00:38:34.300
Most gamblers do things that
they think are revealing of

00:38:34.300 --> 00:38:35.550
their competence.

00:38:35.550 --> 00:38:39.850
And they tend to pick a certain
form of gambling that

00:38:39.850 --> 00:38:42.600
they become psychologically
identified with.

00:38:42.600 --> 00:38:48.020
And they avoid any other
form of gambling.

00:38:48.020 --> 00:38:51.170
Gambling behavior is part
of what goes on

00:38:51.170 --> 00:38:52.760
in the stock market.

00:38:52.760 --> 00:38:55.600
Certain people who have a
personality, which makes them

00:38:55.600 --> 00:39:00.480
particularly interested in
gambling, find that a life in

00:39:00.480 --> 00:39:05.810
finance can give them the
kind of stimulation.

00:39:05.810 --> 00:39:10.330
Gambling behavior, by the way,
is almost like a drug

00:39:10.330 --> 00:39:13.200
addiction in a sense.

00:39:13.200 --> 00:39:18.380
People who are depressed may go
to a gambling casino as a

00:39:18.380 --> 00:39:22.130
way of getting themselves
out of the depression.

00:39:22.130 --> 00:39:25.390
And they say that when they walk
into the casino, suddenly

00:39:25.390 --> 00:39:26.570
my troubles are gone.

00:39:26.570 --> 00:39:30.430
I feel invigorated and alive.

00:39:30.430 --> 00:39:33.610
It's almost like it creates a
hormonal difference that they

00:39:33.610 --> 00:39:36.360
seek, and it's almost like
injecting yourself with

00:39:36.360 --> 00:39:40.090
something, so it's a very
hard thing to conquer.

00:39:40.090 --> 00:39:44.030
I mentioned before, when the New
