a pathology.

00:39:59.410 --> 00:40:03.270
It's an aspect of human
sensation-seeking of various

00:40:03.270 --> 00:40:06.850
aspects of our psychology
that drive us.

00:40:06.850 --> 00:40:10.620
What the stock market is, in
some sense, is a way of

00:40:10.620 --> 00:40:13.960
channeling this kind of behavior
into something

00:40:13.960 --> 00:40:17.090
productive instead
of just a game.

00:40:17.090 --> 00:40:21.530
