in the stock markets of

00:40:21.530 --> 00:40:24.160
the world, this is about
business and this is

00:40:24.160 --> 00:40:25.280
productive.

00:40:25.280 --> 00:40:29.670
The same emotional patterns that
created gambling behavior

00:40:29.670 --> 00:40:33.270
